    "xml": "from turtle import *\n#1、修改两个扇叶的颜色以及风车大小\n#2、补充代码，画出第3个扇叶\n\nsc = Screen()\nsc.bgpic(\"windmill.png\")\nt = Turtle()\nt.shape(\"turtle\")\n#修改颜色以及风车扇叶大小\nt.color(\"red\")\nt.begin_fill()\nt.circle(100,360,3)\nt.end_fill()\nt.left(120)\n\n#修改颜色以及风车扇叶大小\nt.color(\"blue\")\nt.begin_fill()\nt.circle(100,360,3)\nt.end_fill()\nt.left(120)\n\n#在下面补充代码，画出第3个扇叶\nt.color(\"orange\")\nt.begin_fill()\nt.circle(100,360,3)\nt.end_fill()\nt.left(120)\n",
